---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About — NØPE" description="A bit about us.">
  <section class="page-shell layout-shell">
    <div class="page-grid layout-grid">
      <h1 class="page-title visually-hidden">About</h1>
      <div class="about-chunk-1">
        NOPE is a small studio. We make websites, apps, and all things 1s & 0s.
        The name is intentional. We say no to most things. Not out of
        stubbornness, but out of conviction. Most things don't need to exist.
        Extra features nobody asked for. Pages that fill space. Design that
        decorates instead of communicates. Copy that sounds like it was written
        by a committee. We remove all of it. What's left is usually better.
      </div>
      <div class="about-chunk-2">
        This is minimalism, but not as an aesthetic. As a method. Every decision
        starts with a question: does this need to be here? If the answer isn't
        clearly yes, it goes. We apply this to everything. The work we take on,
        the words we write, the pixels we place.
      </div>
      <div class="about-chunk-3">
        We take design seriously. Not as decoration but as communication. The
        typeface, the spacing, the colour, the weight of a line. These are all
        decisions. Decisions made carelessly produce work that feels wrong even
        when people can't say why. We make them carefully. Good design
        disappears. You stop noticing it and start using it.
      </div>
      <div class="about-chunk-4">
        NOPE is very much me. I don't talk if I don't have to. I don't fluff. I
        keep things minimal — in work and in life. The brand isn't a strategy.
        It's just how I think.
        <span class="signature">— Eddie</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .page-title {
      grid-column: 1 / 4;
      font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
      font-weight: var(--font-weight-regular);
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding-top: 0.2em; /* optical alignment with body text */
    }

    .about-chunk-1::first-letter,
    .about-chunk-2::first-letter,
    .about-chunk-3::first-letter,
    .about-chunk-4::first-letter {
      font-size: 3.5em;
      line-height: 0.8;
      float: left;
      margin-right: 0.08em;
      margin-top: 0.05em;
    }

    .about-chunk-1 {
      grid-column: 3 / 8;
      grid-row: 2;
      padding-block: var(--space-12);
    }

    .about-chunk-2 {
      grid-column: 6 / 11;
      grid-row: 3;
      padding-block: var(--space-12);
    }

    .about-chunk-3 {
      grid-column: 3 / 8;
      grid-row: 4;
      padding-block: var(--space-12);
    }

    .about-chunk-4 {
      grid-column: 6 / 11;
      grid-row: 5;
      padding-block: var(--space-12);
    }

    .about-chunk-4::first-letter {
      all: unset;
    }

    .signature {
      display: block;
      margin-top: var(--space-8);
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      font-style: italic;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .about-chunk-1 {
        grid-column: 3 / 9;
      }

      .about-chunk-2 {
        grid-column: 3 / 9;
        grid-row: 3;
        margin-top: var(--space-12);
      }

      .about-chunk-3 {
        grid-column: 3 / 9;
        grid-row: 4;
        margin-top: var(--space-12);
      }

      .about-chunk-4 {
        grid-column: 3 / 9;
        grid-row: 5;
        margin-top: var(--space-12);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about-chunk-1,
      .about-chunk-2,
      .about-chunk-3,
      .about-chunk-4 {
        grid-column: 2 / 12;
      }

      .about-chunk-2,
      .about-chunk-3,
      .about-chunk-4 {
        margin-top: var(--space-10);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .page-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .about-chunk-1,
      .about-chunk-2,
      .about-chunk-3,
      .about-chunk-4 {
        grid-column: 1;
      }

      .about-chunk-2 {
        margin-top: var(--space-6);
      }

      .about-chunk-3 {
        margin-top: var(--space-8);
      }

      .about-chunk-4 {
        margin-top: var(--space-8);
      }

      .page-title {
        margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
